# boutique-webserver - HTTP server for boutique

description "HTTP server for boutique"

start on filesystem
stop on runlevel [!2345]

respawn
respawn limit 10 5
umask 022

pre-start script
    test -x /home/marcenuc/boutique/jake || { stop; exit 0; }
end script

script
  exec su -c 'cd /home/marcenuc/boutique && exec ./jake webserver:start 2>&1 | logger -t boutique-webserver -p local0.error' marcenuc
end script
